🌱 What “Self‑Healing” Really Means in UI/API Automation
A self‑healing agent is simply a smart recovery layer that:

Detects when a locator/API contract breaks

Attempts alternative strategies

Learns from successful fallbacks

Updates the framework so the next run doesn’t fail for the same reason

You don’t need AI models to start — you can build a powerful self‑healing system with structured rules and lightweight heuristics.

⭐ The 5 Easiest & Most Effective Ways to Add Self‑Healing
