3️⃣ API Schema Drift Detection (API Self‑Healing)
For RestAssured, the easiest self‑healing is:

Step 1 — Validate response schema
If schema fails:

Compare expected vs actual keys

Detect added/removed fields

Auto‑update schema if allowed

Or store a diff for review

Step 2 — Auto‑map renamed fields
